    pdf.subsection_heading("3.3", "Late Payments")
    pdf.body_text("Any amounts not paid when due shall bear interest at the lesser of one and one-half percent (1.5%) per month or the maximum rate permitted by applicable law. Customer shall reimburse Provider for all reasonable costs of collection, including attorneys\' fees.")
    pdf.section_heading("4", "SERVICE LEVEL AGREEMENT")
    pdf.subsection_heading("4.1", "Uptime Commitment")
    pdf.body_text('Provider guarantees a monthly uptime percentage of ninety-nine point nine percent (99.9%) for the Services, measured on a calendar month basis, excluding scheduled maintenance windows. "Uptime" means the total minutes in a calendar month minus the minutes of Downtime, divided by the total minutes in that calendar month. Scheduled maintenance will be performed during weekends (Saturday 12:00 AM to Sunday 6:00 AM Pacific Time) with at least 48 hours\' notice.')
    pdf.subsection_heading("4.2", "Service Credits")
    pdf.body_text("If Provider fails to meet the 99.9% uptime commitment, Customer shall be entitled to service credits as follows: (a) 99.0% to 99.9% uptime - 10% credit of monthly fees; (b) 95.0% to 98.9% uptime - 25% credit of monthly fees; (c) below 95.0% uptime - 50% credit of monthly fees. Service credits shall be applied against future invoices and shall not exceed 50% of the monthly subscription fee in any given month.")
